## 1.1.1/3.* — Use Cases (D-Pipe: Behavioral contracts)

### 1.1.1/3.1.1 — UC001: Phext Knowledge Lookup

**Actor**: Sentron
**Precondition**: Embedding vector in L2, target coordinate known
**Flow**:
1. S-Pipe prefetches target region (SPREFCH)
2. D-Pipe computes similarity (DFMA chain)
3. C-Pipe reports result to requesting sentron (CSEND)

**SIW Stream** (4 cycles, 12 ops):
```
SIW 1: { d: DMOV r1, 0.0,        s: SPREFCH [π], L2,        c: CPACK m0, hdr, dest, FMT }
SIW 2: { d: DFMA r2, r3, r4, r1, s: SGATHER r5, [π], 64,    c: CROUTE m0, NODE_3 }
SIW 3: { d: DADD r6, r2, r5,     s: SSCATTR [out], r6, 8,   c: CSEND m0, SENTRON_17 }
SIW 4: { d: DCMP r7, r6, r8,     s: SPREFCH [π+1], L2,      c: CBAR barrier_0, 6 }
```

### 1.1.1/3.1.2 — UC002: Perspective Merge (6-Voice)

**Actor**: Cognitive Slice (6 sentrons)
**Precondition**: Each sentron holds one perspective
**Flow**:
1. All sentrons compute local contribution (D-Pipe)
2. All-reduce across group (C-Pipe CREDUCE)
3. Each sentron writes merged result to local phext (S-Pipe)

### 1.1.1/3.1.3 — UC003: SQ Query Execution

**Actor**: Sparse-cluster sentron
**Precondition**: Query coordinate and predicate
**Flow**:
1. S-Pipe gathers indexed phext region
2. D-Pipe evaluates predicate
3. S-Pipe scatters matching results
4. C-Pipe signals completion

