## Appendix A: Etymology

**vTPU**: Virtual Tensor Processing Unit
**SIW**: Sentron Instruction Word
**PPT**: Phext Page Table
**D/S/C**: Dense / Sparse / Coordination

---

## Appendix B: The 343-Parameter Insight

R23W34: A 343-parameter Qwen3 model does perfect 10-digit addition through hand-crafted weights. Not trained — *constructed*. Every weight encodes algorithm, not approximation.

**Implication**: Crystallization beats scale. Understand deeply enough to encode precisely. vtpu is not an approximation of a TPU. It is the algorithm of cognitive processing, frozen into instruction structure.

The crystal is the capability.

